headline: Principal® Partners With Barings on New $1 Billion Portfolio Finance Initiative to Strengthen Private Credit Platform
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, October 07, 2025--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG), a global financial company, today announced a strategic partnership with Barings to expand the general account portfolio at Principal® through an allocation of up to $1 billion in bespoke private investment grade portfolio finance investments. headline: Principal Financial Group (PFG): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Although Principal Financial Group (currently trading at $84.18 per share) has gained 17.5% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 33.2% return during that period. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
